original_title: 無口な図書委員と、セックス漬け。 七沢みあ
overview: This guy meets a pretty girl working in the school library named Akemi, and he gets mesmerized by her beauty and by her misterious aura.  He begins to visit the school library with the sole purpose of approaching her. Despite her very cold reactions, he doesn’t give up, and finally, he notices something weird about her…
title: Hardcore Sex With A Quiet Librarian student – Mia Nanasawa
